<style><style><style><style><style><style><style>
html::before {
    content: "";
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: orange;
    display: block;
}
p { writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    contain: layout;
}
</style></style></style></style></style></style></style>

<p><p><p><p><p>Test passes if the orange square is in the upper-left corner.
